title: Title Page, "Sest Dob Nashi Historie," Portfolio, Prague, 1921
description:
Title page with vignette of coat of arms with rampant lion, on large sheet which is folded so as to form a last page as well, on which is imprinted the colophon and titles of Plates I through VI.
(See description field for 6548.20 for general portfolio information.)
